t/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2760147005/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2760147005","tinyui":"/x/PYCEp","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2760147005","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2760147005/Iniciativas+en+Curso","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2760147005"}},{"id":"2685665290","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2685665290","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjY4NTY2NTI5MA==","status":"current","title":"Ruby Upgrade","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":10596421},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2685665290/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2685665290/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2685665290/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2685665290/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2685665290","tinyui":"/x/CgAUo","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2685665290","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2685665290/Ruby+Upgrade","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2685665290"}},{"id":"4470308902","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/4470308902","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvNDQ3MDMwODkwMg==","status":"current","title":"Archived - Ruby Upgrade","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":36961847},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/4470308902/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/4470308902/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/4470308902/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/4470308902/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/4470308902","tinyui":"/x/JoBzCgE","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=4470308902","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/4470308902/Archived+-+Ruby+Upgrade","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/4470308902"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<p>Dentro de estas estimaciones tuvimos en cuenta el esfuerzo dedicado a la actualizaci&oacute;n de Ruby y las gemas que se utilizan, teniendo en cuenta la compatibilidad de las mismas, cambios en las gemas nuestras o la b&uacute;squeda de alternativas para suplantarlas. Tambi&eacute;n una etapa de testeo de la funcionalidad de otros servicios y plataformas/portales que interact&uacute;an con &eacute;l. No est&aacute; contemplado las posibles mejoras y errores conocidos que pueda proponer el equipo de Bancard.</p><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"e1ebfd45-a143-4b68-99c1-c0d5a4067df3\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 127.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 91.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 99.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 303.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 140.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Service</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Min Est (Days) </strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Max Est (Days)</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Comments</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Prioridad</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>audit-service</p></td><td><p>20</p></td><td><p>30</p></td><td><p>Hay que actualizar todo. Es un proyecto que est&aacute; al d&iacute;a y no deber&iacute;a generar mucho desaf&iacute;o.</p></td><td><p>5</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>auth-service</p></td><td><p>7</p></td><td><p>14</p></td><td><p>Ya est&aacute; actualizado. Requiere algunas mejoras</p></td><td><p>1 </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>biller-service</p></td><td><p>14</p></td><td><p>20</p></td><td><p>Es un servicio chico con gemas bastante standard dentro de los servicios que tenemos</p></td><td><p>2</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>billing-service</p></td><td><p>20</p></td><td><p>30</p></td><td><p>A confirmar si hay que actualizar o ya es compatible para darle una prioridad</p></td><td><p>3</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>loyalty-service</p></td><td><p>??? </p></td><td><p>???</p></td><td><p>A confirmar porque es un proyecto que esta desactualizado y sin mantenimiento. Puede llevar mucho tiempo. Habr&iacute;a que estimarlo con Gian, o hablarlo con &eacute;l al menos para tener una mejor comprensi&oacute;n del funcionamiento de los flujos y procesos.</p></td><td><p>muy baja</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>mpos-service</p></td><td><p>30</p></td><td><p>45</p></td><td><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Arreglar GitHub actions que no est&aacute;n funcionando</p></li><li><p>Usa gemas particulares, como unas custom (tlv, dukpt, rqrcode) que no tienen mucha o nula documentaci&oacute;n y hay que entender mejor el contexto.</p></li><li><p>Es un proyecto que est&aacute; un poco deprectado. Hay que hablar con Bancard a ver si lo quiere actualizar</p></li></ol></td><td><p>7</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>s4-service</p></td><td><p>14</p></td><td><p>20</p></td><td><p>Es un proyecto chico que aloja rutas de archivos.</p></td><td><p>6</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>vpos-service</p></td><td><p>20</p></td><td><p>30</p></td><td><ul><li><p>Tiene un portal asociado que es  VPos Portal</p></li><li><p>Actualizar VPos service es sencillo, pero si tenemos que tocar VPos portal habr&iacute;a que asignarle bastante m&aacute;s. (Si hay que sumar VPos Portal, necestar&iacute;amos sumar a <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"612e2e8063f7bb006976b761\" /></ac:link> a la estimaci&oacute;n que es el que sabe m&aacute;s del tema)</p></li></ul></td><td><p>4</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>vpos-portal (Nice To Have)</p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p>VPos portal no es un servicio por lo tanto no afectar&iacute;a noa ctualizarlo, pero estar&iacute;a bueno hacerlo en alg&uacute;n momento.</p><ul><li><p>Si hay que sumar VPos Portal, necestar&iacute;amos sumar a <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"612e2e8063f7bb006976b761\" /></ac:link> a la estimaci&oacute;n que es el que sabe m&aacute;s del tema)</p></li></ul></td><td><p>a confirmar</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><em>Estimaci&oacute;n m&iacute;nima</em>: <strong>119 d&iacute;as </strong></p><p><em>Estimaci&oacute;n m&aacute;xima</em>: <strong>179 d&iacute;as</strong></p><p>Estas estimaciones no incluyen a loyalty-service y vpos-portal. Habr&iacute;a que confirmar primero si se quieren actualizar, y en ese caso con <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"557058:c3ef74c9-1ae0-468d-8526-13a6cda5d7e5\" /></ac:link> y <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"612e2e8063f7bb006976b761\" /></ac:link> respectivamente.</p>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/2808250461"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":51783016},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2808250461/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2808250461/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2808250461/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2808250461/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2808250461","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2808250461/Ruby+Upgrade+-+Estimations","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2808250461","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2808250461","tinyui":"/x/XYBipw","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}